<h2 id="org4e6d8df">What is the task?</h2>
<p>
📝
</p>

<p>
Build the data reading compute part for a Data Ingestion Pipeline.
</p>

<p>
In other words:
</p>

<p>
Load training dataset stored in an S3 bucket to an EC2 machine ready for training.
</p>
</section><div class="slide-number slide-number-pdf">3</div></div><div class="pdf-page" style="height: 727px; background: rgb(17, 17, 17);"><div class="slide-background present" style="display: block;" data-loaded="true"><div class="slide-background-content"></div></div><section id="slide-org9cbd6c4" hidden="" aria-hidden="true" class="present" style="display: block; left: 19px; top: 237.5px; width: 960px;">
