</p>

<ul>
<li class="fragment appear visible current-fragment" data-fragment-index="0">Just needs the length calculation and the <span class="underline"><span class="underline">iter</span></span> functionality</li>
<li class="fragment appear" data-fragment-index="1">Inherits pytorch Dataset class as parent so it's automatically compatible with pytorch</li>

</ul>

